useCase.name: Append a value to a list

action.precondition: ac.this = leaf and leaf.next = null and leaf.isLeaf = true and ac.x = node and node <> leaf
action.postcondition: leaf.next = node and ac.x = null and leaf.isLeaf = false and node.isLeaf = true

action.precondition: ac.this = nfrom and nfrom.next = nto and ac.x = node and node <> nfrom
ac.this = listnode and ac.x = node and node = listnode
